data.description: Newer home built in 2019 with 3 spacious Bedrooms and large master suite, 3 bathrooms; 2 car garage, home office, Covered front porch, covered patio ideal for Colorado indoor/outdoor living, and 3/4 unfinished basement. The main floor features a home office at the front of the home with a powder bath. The chef’s kitchen features espresso 42-inch cabinets, a kitchen island, granite countertops, a pantry, a gas range, and stainless steel appliances! Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main floor. Open floor plan great room, dining room, kitchen. Sliding glass doors out to the covered patio and backyard. Convenient second-floor laundry room, washer/dryer included!!! Plus, full wall of extra upper and lower cabinets with folding countertops! All 4 bedrooms upstairs! Beautiful spacious primary suite with built-in speakers, can lighting and ceiling fan prewire. En-suite primary bathroom with 2 sinks and lots of countertop space, walk-in shower with tile detail, and frameless glass shower door. Dreamy walk-in closet! 3 secondary bedrooms, plus a hallway full bathroom with 2 sinks and bathtub, 2 sinks with spacious vanity granite countertop, and lots of under cabinet storage. full unfinished basement. the full unfinished basement. Crystal Valley Ranch of Castle Rock offers incredible amenities to enjoy! Pinnacle Park Recreation Center with pool, fitness center, and community room, multiple parks and trails throughout the community, designated dog park, open space, tennis court, soccer field, Quarry Mesa Open Space trails, and MORE! Just a 5-minute drive to the Town of Castle Rock, Phillip S Miller Park, Outlets at Castle Rock Shopping! radon system in place.
